product_description:
The AMX-104 R-Jarja, the prototype mobile suit for commanders from "Gundam ZZ," gets a HGUC kit from Bandai! Special attention has been paid to accurately reproducing its proportions and color, and ensuring a wide range of motion for action poses; it's equipped with its distinctive heat bayonet/beam rifle and large beam saber. Get yours today!
[Includes]:

Heat bayonet + beam rifle
Large beam saber
Foil stickers
